==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Hey
<hw>Hey</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>interj.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>hei</ets>;
cf. D. & G. <ets>hei</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An exclamation of
joy, surprise, or encouragement.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A cry to set dogs on.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Heyday</ent>⟦br⟧
